shape_description

Amphora of type A with lid, but special model. The amphora is abnormal both in its general shape and its details, such as the form of the foot and the decoration of the handles. Only Berlin F 3210 (ABV, 151, 21) has the same shape. Wrzburg L 282 is its correspondent lid.
